                                                                        </li>
                                                                    </ul>
                                                                </div>
                                                                <p>
                                                                    NEW YORK, NY, February 29, 2024 – Gold Level Sports &amp; Entertainment (GLSE) and the National Basketball Players Association (NBPA) are continuing their partnership to bring back the second edition of their highly successful high school basketball event, The Throne, on March 27-30 at the American Dream entertainment/retail center in East Rutherford, New Jersey. This four-day single elimination bracket tournament gives the top high school teams in the country an opportunity to compete for the highest title, a national championship, with all games airing on national television. New this year, The Throne will also feature a women&#39;s tournament with eight of the country&#39;s top high school basketball teams.


                                                                </p>
