                                                                    <h3>
                                                                        NBPA, JAKOB POELTL, AND GABE DANON COME TOGETHER TO RELAUNCH ONLINE GUESSING GAME &#34;POELTL&#34;
                                                                    </h3>
                                                                </a>
                                                                <div class="post-opt fl-wrap">
                                                                    <ul style="margin-left: 0px;">
                                                                        <li><i class="fal fa-calendar-alt"></i>
                                                                            February 08, 2024
                                                                        </li>
                                                                    </ul>
                                                                </div>
                                                                <p>
                                                                    NEW YORK, NY, February 8, 2024 - The National Basketball Players Association (NBPA), Jakob Poeltl, and Gabe Danon are teaming up to relaunch &#34;Poeltl,&#34; a daily online guessing game that tests fans knowledge of their favorite NBPA members. First launched in February 2022 by founder Gabe Danon and named after current NBPA member Jakob Poeltl, Poeltl was inspired by the impact of popular daily online puzzle games and gives users eight (8) attempts to guess a mystery NBA player of the day.  


                                                                </p>
