                                                                    <h3>
                                                                        THE NBPA&#39;S BROTHERHOOD DELI IMMERSIVE RETAIL EXPERIENCE SET TO POP UP IN INDIANAPOLIS DURING ALL-STAR WEEKEND
                                                                    </h3>
                                                                </a>
                                                                <div class="post-opt fl-wrap">
                                                                    <ul style="margin-left: 0px;">
                                                                        <li><i class="fal fa-calendar-alt"></i>
                                                                            January 31, 2024
                                                                        </li>
                                                                    </ul>
                                                                </div>
                                                                <p>
                                                                    New York, NY, January 31, 2024 – The NBPA, through its partnership and innovation engine, THINK450, announced the debut of its NBPA Brotherhood Deli fan pop-up shop at All-Star weekend this year in Indianapolis. Presented by Chase Freedom, the NBPA Brotherhood Deli is an immersive retail experience that will be open to the public from February 16-19 at the Circle Centre Mall on the 2nd floor (units E15-E16). First launched on the concourse of the Thomas &amp; Mack Center in the summer of 2023, the NBPA&#39;s Brotherhood Deli pop-up shop gives fans an opportunity to shop and discover brands founded by, invested in, respected, or endorsed by NBPA members.




