                                                        <article>
                                                            <div class="col-md-12">
                                                                <a href="/news/nbpa-announces-andre-iguodala-as-acting-executive-director">
                                                                    <h3>
                                                                        NBPA ANNOUNCES ANDRE IGUODALA AS ACTING EXECUTIVE Director
                                                                    </h3>
                                                                </a>
                                                                <div class="post-opt fl-wrap">
                                                                    <ul style="margin-left: 0px;">
                                                                        <li><i class="fal fa-calendar-alt"></i>
                                                                            November 09, 2023
                                                                        </li>
                                                                    </ul>
                                                                </div>
                                                                <p>
                                                                    NEW YORK, NY, November 9, 2023 – The Executive Committee of the National Basketball Players Association (NBPA) announced today that they are appointing Andre Iguodala as Acting Executive Director. Iguodala will assume all duties and responsibilities of the Executive Director effective immediately. Iguodala is replacing Tamika Tremaglio, who had served in the role since January 2021, and is stepping down from the position to pursue new opportunities after successfully leading the Union through the latest round of collective bargaining with the League earlier this year.
                                                                </p>
                                                                <a href="/news/nbpa-announces-andre-iguodala-as-acting-executive-director"
